Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================TEXT================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六年不見 但是很快就認出帚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:50.11,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(912,215)}{\fad(0,1500)}班代表決定戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 關於你的IS 可能要花點時間才能準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有預備的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以學校會替你準備好專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專用機？給一年級的? 而且還是在這個時期?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那是由政府出錢支持的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害… 我也想早點擁有專用機啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有專用機很牛麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到這個 我就安心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班代表決定戰 雖然我和你勝負早就顯現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要是用專用機 而你用訓練機 實在是太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也擁有專用機了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我教導身為庶民的你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 塞西莉婭·奧盧卡多 是英國的代表候補生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我現在就已經擁有專用機了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上總共僅有467台IS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中能夠擁有專用機的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全人類六十多億的人口中 便是屬於精英中的精英哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有467台嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS其製作技術的核心部分卻完全沒有公開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(584,649)\fs30}Core
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在世界上所見到的467台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的核心部分全都是筱之之束博士所製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是帚的姐姐麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS核心 完全被黑盒化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了筱之之博士之外 沒有人能夠製作核心部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 由於博士始終拒絕製作超乎一定數量的核心部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在各國家 企業 組織 機關便使用各自分配到的核心 來進行研究 開發 訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本IS專用機是只能給隸屬於國家或企業的人使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於你是例外中的例外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要收集資料 才會替你準備專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你理解了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 大致上懂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 請問一下 筱之之同學難道和筱之之博士有關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們班的筱之之  是那傢伙的親妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  原來還是個姐姐啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱之之博士不是現在行蹤不明 各國政府 企業都在尋找嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡你不知道麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那個人沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那個人  也沒有什麼可告訴你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田老師 請繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就繼續上課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚和束關係有那麼差麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天接昨天的繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS  Infinite Stratos
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控者的全身會被特殊的能源防護罩包覆起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(797,639)\fs30}Energy Barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而IS像有意識一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此之間的對話 就是說 要通過共同度過的時間來相互瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著操縱時間比例的增加 IS那邊也能夠開始理解操控者的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS並不是道具 大家記得要把它當作夥伴來看待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有誰要提問麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 當作夥伴 那就像是男女朋友的那種感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這個嘛  該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有經驗  所以不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會 會是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞啦 老師真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的女子學校的勢頭…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱之之同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有其他人要一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然有帶便當 可是也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然同班同學就應該好好相處嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 站起來 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我說我不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想走路嗎 要我背你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變厲害了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 是你變弱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種動作只是劍術的附屬品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說過別叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你不要太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖跟著就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要那麼生氣吧 虧我還那麼擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拜託你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平時的話 即使被人拜託也不會做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是帚 所以我才肯這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母他們總是很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是我的青梅竹馬兼劍道同門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候我總該雞婆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個… 謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你點的兩份當日套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚 你有看到哪裡有空位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那邊有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有做錯什麼了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  帚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以教我關於IS的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去 下周的決鬥我只能舉手投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你要被無聊的挑釁給煽動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我想想辦法啦 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你是傳聞中的那個男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你要和一個代表候補生比賽 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你是門外漢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我來教你呢 關於IS的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 因為我已經說好要教他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一年級的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來教會比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是筱之之束的妹妹 所以不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就沒辦法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意教我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 就算你問我是怎麼一回事 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會弱成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你國中參加什麼社團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸家部 連續三年都是全勤獎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新調教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些可都是在談IS之前的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 每天放學後我會監督你練習3小時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 IS的事怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了 這是排在IS之前的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學他啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實蠻弱的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的有啟動過IS嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是說得太過分了一點啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那樣正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很明顯是將近一年沒握過竹刀的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 他不可能會像那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會那樣輸給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六年 六年不見 他那個樣子 變得如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 明天開始放學後就要開始特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 放學後就能和一夏單獨…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不是在想那樣的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是單純的基於同門的份上幫他一把而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以堂堂正正！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  帚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過要教我IS的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准把眼睛移開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周 除了劍道之外什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒辦法啊 因為你的IS還沒送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有IS 你可以教我一些知識或基本的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 不准把眼睛移開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是她的專用機麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學 織斑同學 織斑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送來了 織斑同學的專用IS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 立刻去做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競技場的使用時間可是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就硬著頭皮 闖闖看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是織斑同學的專用IS 「白式」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去著裝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在實戰中做格式化和設定最佳化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,639)\fs30}format
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(853,639)\fs30}fitting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第一次接觸IS時的感覺完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 織斑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼… 問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉 並且能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西是什麼 它是為了什麼而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把背靠上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣 像是坐著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統會自動最佳化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,access
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,system start
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白式 這就是白式麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞的機體是「藍色之淚」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(817,639)\fs30}blue tears
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠距離射擊型的IS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色之淚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS具有「絕對防禦」能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以阻擋一切攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差的情況 也會保護操控者的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻會極端地消耗防護能源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,639)\fs30}Shield Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 有沒有不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我等你勝利歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你最後一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會是我單方面獲得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就在這裡向我道歉 那麼我也不是不能原諒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種要求並不叫機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎? 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告! 敵機IS進入射擊姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟不上白式的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著我塞西莉婭·奧盧卡多與藍色之淚所奏出的華爾茲起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護能源在不斷地被削減
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備呢 有什麼裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這一個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比什麼都沒有強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想用近距離的格鬥裝備 來對抗遠距離射擊型的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可笑之極
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這架藍色之淚面前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我頭一次看到能夠撐得這麼久的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我們進入終場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左腳 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兵器每一次都要接收你的指令才會做出動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法進行其他的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須集中意識去控制它們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…織斑同學很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人無法想像這居然是第二次操縱IS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢蛋正在得意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的左手就一直在握拳打開 握拳又打開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這個習慣動作出現時 他通常就會犯下低級錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦… 真不愧是姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩隻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會瞄準我反應最慢的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離近了 就是對我有利了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上當嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不僅僅4個呦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 被機體救了一命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑同學的專用機形狀改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「格式化」「設定最佳化」完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難 難道是……初次轉換
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(781,639)\fs30}First shift
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才只用了初期設定的機體在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然完全搞不清什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道 這下這台機體終於變成我的專用了的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近戰特化刀 「雪片貳型」可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪片貳型…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪片不是千冬姐用的武器麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我真是擁有世界上最棒的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我差不多也該結束掉這種一味被保護的關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要守護我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 得先保住千冬姐的名聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟的能力太差 那就太沒面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真是的 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝者  塞西莉婭·奧盧卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  為什麼輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你使用了 防護罩無效化攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你根本不考慮武器的特性就去使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護罩無效化…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過撕裂對方的防護罩從而直接對本體造成直接傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪片的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過消耗自身防護罩能量而轉化的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 之所以我能坐上世界第一的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能力功不可沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以白式防護罩的剩餘能量瞬間就變成0了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS的戰鬥中 防護罩的能量變為0 就視為輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護罩無效化攻擊 是用自己防護罩的能量 給對方傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比喻的話 就是以身做刃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你的IS是有缺陷機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺陷機？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的說法不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS本來就是未完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也就沒有所謂的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的機體只是比其他機體在攻擊方面稍微特殊化了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS現在雖然進入了待機狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要織斑同學你一呼叫 它立刻就能展開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在這方面上是有規則的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你要好好熟讀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS教則書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她就是班代表了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了 很不甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始 那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要開始IS的訓練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 一夏還是想讓我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 相比其他女生感覺應該會好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你是束的妹妹 IS又很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就讓我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天開始 放學後的時間絕對要空下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這種心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個女孩是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.55,0:23:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和織斑同學關係那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是從中國來的專用機操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是織斑中學時的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣也是班代表
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班級戰會和織斑同學交手的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 轉校生是第二個青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(190,250)\fs60}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(640,480)\shad5\fs60}「轉校生是第二個青梅竹馬」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.21,0:24:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 像旗袍樣式的IS會不會出現啊 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能 不能  絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
